lead_paragraph: Atletico Madrid surrendered top spot in La Liga to Barcelona when they were held 0-0 at home by 10-man Sevilla on Sunday before Real Madrid lost ground after an entertaining 1-1 stalemate at Real Betis.

headline.print_headline: Atletico Cede Top Spot to Barca, Real Held
